{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八回　万相真人：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第八回万相真人鄂省一地，湖泊独多，本为古云梦大泽旧迹，他两人遇着湖泊，便不免要绕远些路途，何况他两人湖北境的北部，俱未到过，沿途问向，也不免耽误了时候，尚未明知道熊倜心急，便提议昼伏夜行，以便夜间可以施展轻功，熊倜自大喜称是。过汉水，两人连夜赶前，夜色苍茫中，熊倜远远望见前面山势横亘，他两人轻功超绝，艺高胆大，也不顾忌什么，黑夜中便闯上章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才我慌忙中蹿进这山谷……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你有没有看到谷口的石碑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谷口还有个石碑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快朝来路退。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两个娃娃跑到我这甜甜谷来，还想出去吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，又出了什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_uboye",
      "speaker_name": "气",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敏敏",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你又来了，你……你是不是想我的这副样子给别人看了……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道两位此刻必定疑团重重，而且我看两位俱都身怀绝技，可是许多年来，只要入此谷中的人，从没有一个能全身而退，两位自也不例外……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位既是知道我的名字，那再好也没有，我今日权且做主，只要两位留下两样东西来，便可走出此谷……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubeyp_ubupt",
      "speaker_name": "冷笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敏敏",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不然，你们就得把命留下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要动手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，快动手嘛，还跟他罗嗦什么。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你先让我一个人试试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubupt",
      "speaker_name": "笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敏敏",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林中怎地出了个这样的好手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubwdf_ubwdf",
      "speaker_name": "缓缓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敏敏",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，我就出手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位兄台可是姓熊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢，小弟正是熊倜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台宠召，不敢不从命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里便是寒舍了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位稍候，我去去就来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敏妹，你怎么……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，你真好……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_xiang_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万相真人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下之大，哪有女婿要找岳父拼命的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，女儿从此一定听你老人家的话，爹爹你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恭喜常兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，我们该走了吧。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位千万要在此盘桓些时日，怎地现在就要走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既有这等事，小弟也不敢再多留两位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    }
  ],
